OL,4,Cdeleted WhatsApp messages during
OL,5,Cpandemic
OL,7,FA senior government official has
OL,8,Fadmitted to setting WhatsApp messages
OL,9,Fto automatically delete during the
OL,10,Fpandemic against Welsh Government
OL,11,Fadvice, an inquiry has heard.
OL,13,FJane Runeckles, a special adviser for
OL,14,Fthe Welsh Government, was speaking in
OL,15,FCardiff at the Inquiry on Thursday, 7
OL,16,FMarch.
OL,18,FShe admitted to using the
OL,19,F"disappearing messages" function on
OL,20,Fthe messaging app during the
OL,21,Fcoronavirus pandemic.
