OL,7,FMs Runeckles has worked for the
OL,8,FGovernment for almost 20 years and is
OL,9,Fthe most senior adviser to the First
OL,10,FMinister Mark Drakeford.
OL,12,FShe ultimately accepted she was using
OL,13,Fthe technology "wrongly". Welsh
OL,14,FGovernment guidance said that personal
OL,15,FWhatsApp accounts should not be used
OL,16,Fand that using messaging tools was
OL,17,Fcreating "public records."
