OL,7,FWhen asked if she was aware that using
OL,8,FWhatsApp for decision-making was
OL,9,Fprohibited, Ms Runeckles said she
OL,10,F"knew that (she) was not in a position
OL,11,Fto use (her) personal phone for Welsh
OL,12,FGovernment formal decision-making".
OL,14,FHowever, she argued that the groups
OL,15,Fwere only used for "admin purposes and
OL,16,Ffor team morale".
OL,18,FLady Hallett, the chair of the inquiry
OL,19,Fasked: "Isn't using your personal
OL,20,Fphone for admin purposes using it for
OL,21,FWelsh Government business?
