OL,7,F"So, you were using it wrongly?"
OL,9,FMs Runeckles replied: "Yes."
OL,11,FWhen asked why she used disappearing
OL,12,Fmessages, the special advisor told the
OL,13,Finquiry that she did not believe there
OL,14,Fwas any evidence of decision-making in
OL,15,Fthe groups.
OL,17,FShe added that "it would be very
OL,18,Fuseful for people who hold the kind of
OL,19,Frole that I hold in the future for
OL,20,Fthere to be some clear recommendations
OL,21,Fabout this".
