OL,7,FAn earlier hearing was told that
OL,8,Fspecial advisers reminded themselves
OL,9,Fand others that they had agreed "to
OL,10,Fclear out WhatsApp chat once a week".
OL,12,FIt has not been made clear by the
OL,13,Finquiry who said this and Ms Runckles
OL,14,Fwas not questioned about the advice.
OL,16,FThe inquiry is set to continue next
OL,17,Fweek where Vaughan Gething, who was
OL,18,Fhealth minister at the time, Mark
OL,19,FDrakeford, and Eluned Morgan are among
OL,20,Fthose set to give evidence.
